# {{SERVICE_NAME}} - LLM Graph Builder

Build knowledge graphs from documents using LLMs.

## Features

- Document ingestion and chunking
- Entity and relationship extraction via LLMs
- Neo4j graph storage
- Natural language querying

## Requirements

- Neo4j database (added automatically if not present)
- OpenAI or OpenRouter API key

## Environment Variables

Required (set in .env.secrets):
- `OPENAI_API_KEY` or `OPENROUTER_API_KEY`
- `NEO4J_PASSWORD`

## Usage

Access the web UI at: http://localhost:{{SERVICE_PORT}}

